data.description: Welcome to 1130 Tanner Cir, a charming single family home located in Blackshear, GA. Built in 2008, this well-maintained property offers a comfortable and inviting space for you to call home. Boasting a total of  1,356 sq.ft. of finished living area, this home provides ample space for you and your family to enjoy.Situated on a spacious lot spanning 14,375 sq.ft., there is plenty of room for outdoor activities and entertaining guests. The exterior of the home features a lovely curb appeal with a well-manicured lawn and landscaping. The backyard offers a peaceful retreat with the potential for creating your own outdoor oasis.As you step inside, you are greeted with a warm and inviting interior. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, perfect for everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a breakfast bar for casual dining.The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of natural light, creating a comfortable and relaxing atmosphere. The bathrooms are well-appointed with modern fixtures and finishes, providing a spa-like experience.Additional features of this home include a laundry room, storage space, and a two-car garage for added convenience. The property is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining options, making it an ideal location for your next home.Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience all that 1130 Tanner Cir has to offer.
